      "date": "2012-06-22 21:06:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b605678a-bcad-11e1-9c6f-52540035b04c).  Ran 4 tests.  1 tests failed: scrub-performance.",
