        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-06-23 05:08:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe failure may be caused by improper cleanup of former sanity-scrub. I have updated related scripts. I have moved the autotest to former patch(http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3168), in which the scripts are introduced.",
